cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Private AI Platform Kit in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "Private AI Platform Kit"
abstract: >-
  A runnable Kubernetes platform stack for private LLMs, RAG, and coding-agent
  workspaces. It starts on a local kind cluster with Ollama and uses the same
  Helm charts, GitOps layout, policies, runbooks, and evidence checks on
  customer-owned clusters with vLLM and GPU nodes.
type: software
